== PathLab — Shared Database Path Configuration ==

Is file ka naam badlo: db_path.txt (example hata do)

Pehli line = database file ka full path
Doosri line = media folder ka full path (logos, signatures)

---
WINDOWS EXAMPLES:

Pendrive (drive E:):
E:\pathlab_data\db.sqlite3
E:\pathlab_data\media

Network Server:
\\192.168.1.100\shared\pathlab\db.sqlite3
\\192.168.1.100\shared\pathlab\media

---
LINUX EXAMPLES:

/mnt/pendrive/pathlab/db.sqlite3
/mnt/pendrive/pathlab/media

---
NOTE:
- Agar yeh file nahi hai toh default project folder mein db.sqlite3 use hoga
- start.bat mein PATHLAB_DB_PATH set karna zyada reliable hai
- Ek hi db file ko multiple computers simultaneously use nahi kar sakte (SQLite limitation)
  Iske liye MySQL/PostgreSQL use karein ya ek machine ko server banao aur baaki browser se kholen
